Belmoral Mines Ltd agree principle 26 mln dlr sale mln unit price 6.50 dlrs investment dealer McLeod Young Weir Ltd subject board regulatory approvals. Holders allow exchange unit September 15 1987 common share common share purchase warrant Belmoral company said. Each warrant holder purchase Belmoral common share 8.50 dlrs January 15 1990. McLeod Young Weir plan resell unit institutional private investor mainly Europe Belmoral said. Reuter 